      "description": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "\"EXPERIENCE THE JOY OF CREATION\"Create beautiful, gallery-worthy masterpieces using the magic of motion.Step into a creative journey and rediscover the joy of painting.Everyone is an artist at Motion Art Space, no art skill needed!Motion Art Space is the first motion art experience in the world that started from Singapore! Combining art with science, we provide a safe and fun space for you to experiment and express your creativity.All the necessary materials, including canvases, paint, brushes, tools, and aprons are provided. We have a 5 minutes video instruction and it will be a free and easy session thereafter.How to get there:MRT STATIONS:• Bugis (10 mins)• Nicoll Highway (9 mins)BUSES:10, 100, 107, 57, 961• Beach Road – Opposite Plaza Parkroyal (01521) (2 mins)• Ophir Road – Opposite Duo Residences (01549) (3 mins)• North Bridge Road – Parkview Square (01139) (6 mins)PARKING SPOTS (Car lots may be limited at Arab St):• Golden Landmark Shopping Complex - 390 Victoria St, Singapore 188061 (5 mins walk)• Arab Street/ Queen Street Car Park (A0017) (7 mins walk)• City Gate - 371 Beach Road, Singapore 199597 (10 mins walk)"
          }
        ]
      },
