                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "\"EXPERIENCE FOR ALL AGES,&nbsp;PLAY &amp; CONNECT\"&nbsp;Exhilarating 1-hour experience. Create unforgettable memories with dates, friends, and family. Experiment with new techniques in a fun environment! Everyone is an artist at Motion Art Space! No artistic skill or experience is required to create your very own masterpiece. Instructions are provided at the space, or you are free to explore your creativity!"
